        Match time.
        [match:test]
            =a
                (correct) match hit a here.
        [/match]
    ?: Agreed & Match that fails
        Okay, sequence here.
        Match time.
        [match:test]
            =fail
                We should not see this
        [/match]
}
This is the fallback of the option, the match should still hit this.
